Swan Chain
A Full Toolset AI Blockchain
Swan Chain, initiated in 2021, is a full toolset AI blockchain infrastructure accelerating AI adoption. Utilizing OP Stack's Ethereum Layer 2 technology, it pioneers in merging Web3 with AI by providing comprehensive solutions across storage, computing, bandwidth, and payments.

Components of Swan Chain

Edge Computing Provider

Edge Computing Provider specializes in processing data at the source of data generation, using minimal latency setups ideal for real-time applications.

Fog Computing Provider

Offers a layered network that extends cloud capabilities to the edge of the network, providing services such as AI model training and deployment.

Market Provider

A platform that facilitates the allocation of computing jobs to providers, utilizing an auction engine for job distribution and a payment engine for financial transactions.

Advantages of Swan Chain's AI computing network

Cost-Efficient

Reduce AI computing costs by up to 70% through our decentralized marketplace.

Global Reach

Access AI computing resources in over 100 locations worldwide.

Instant Deployment

Launch your AI workloads within minutes using our user-friendly interface.

ZK Powerhouse

Leverage our global zero-knowledge(ZK) Market for privacy-preserving AI model training

Fair Incentives

Benefit from our UBI-based node incentive mechanism for a balanced token economy.
